The '''Sesseranda Ocean''' was a major body of water on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Kothlis/Legends|Kothlis]]. It became polluted during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]] when the major company [[Plextech Plastic Corporation]] began to dump its noxious by-products into its depths.

